Kitest optional package groups (formerly Calamares netinstall bundles)

Reference list: ../netinstall-bundles.yaml

These JSON files contain only a "packages" array. Merge them into a full configuration
from `archinstall` (use "Save configuration" in the TUI), or add the same package names
under Additional packages in the guided installer.

Example:

  archinstall --config /usr/share/kitest/archinstall-examples/development.json

You may need a complete user_configuration.json from a dry run; merge the "packages" key.

Brave browser: install from Flathub on the live session or after install:

  flatpak install flathub com.brave.Browser

Catppuccin in Brave is usually a theme from the Chrome Web Store (manual step).
